movie.title: Death of a Superhero
movie.description_intro: A dying 15-year-old boy draws stories of an invincible superhero as he struggles with his mortality.
movie.description_full: A dying 15-year-old boy draws stories of an invincible superhero as he struggles with his mortality.

movies.title: Skateboard or Die
movies.summary: Mike, an easygoing military dropout is thrust into a hidden world of murder and assassination after running into his best friend Ed, after 10 years of thinking he was Killed In Action. In order to save Mike's fiancee Sarah and keep themselves alive, Mike and Ed must now work together as members of - The Hunters Club. 'The Hunters Club' is a gun toting, fist fighting, skateboarding, independent action flick, shot in Brisbane and the Gold Coast Qld, Australia.

movies.title: Free to Play
movies.summary: Follow three professional video game players as they overcome personal adversity, family pressures, and the realities of life to compete in a $1,000,000 tournament that could change their lives forever.

movies.title: Kingdom Come
movies.summary: A group of strangers who wake up in what appears to be an abandoned building, unable to remember how they got there, find themselves haunted by strange visions and are forced to face all the wrongs they have done in their lives.

movies.title: A Bay of Blood
movies.summary: An elderly heiress is killed by her husband who wants control of her fortunes. What ensues is an all-out murder spree as relatives and friends attempt to reduce the inheritance playing field, complicated by some teenagers who decide to camp out in a dilapidated building on the estate.
